## **.gitignore**

Crie um arquivo chamado `.gitignore` na raiz do seu projeto e adicione o seguinte conte√∫do:

```gitignore
# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# C extensions
*.so

# Distribution / packaging
.Python
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg

# Virtual environment
venv/
env/
ENV/
env.bak/
venv.bak/

# Jupyter Notebook
.ipynb_checkpoints

# PyCharm
.idea/

# VS Code
.vscode/

# Logs
*.log

# Data files
*.csv
*.xlsx

# Environment variables
.env
.env.*
